SUMMARY:GTApreneurs April 28-2026 Business Networking Event Vaughan - Toro
 nto
DESCRIPTION:Toronto Women in Business Networking Group (TWIB)\nJoin us for
  an exciting Business Networking Event in Vaughan\, just north of Toronto 
 on Tuesday April 28\, 2026 where you can meet potential clients and referr
 al partners\, learn something new\, enjoy a meal and promote your business
 !\n\n**REGISTER HERE:** https://gtapreneurs.com/networking-events-vaughan\
 n\n**VENUE:** Canadian Blood Services\, Donor Centre\n**ADDRESS:** 200 Win
 dflower Gate\, Woodbridge\, ON L4L 9L3\n**PARKING:** Free\, onsite.\n\nFoo
 d and beverages provided.\n\n**EVENT ITINERARY:**\n\n* **5:00-6:00pm:** Op
 en networking\, food buffet\, visit exhibitor booths\n* **6:00-6:10pm:** G
 TApreneurs welcoming presentation\n* **6:10-6:30pm:** Featured Speaker Pre
 sentation\, “***Experience What You Get When You Give: Partnering with C
 anadian Blood Services***.”\n* **6:30-7:00pm:** Exhibitor Introductions 
 + member Elevator Pitches\n* **7:00-8:00pm:** Open networking\, visit exhi
 bitor booths\n\n**TICKETS**\n\n* **GTApreneurs' Referral Group\, Exhibitor
  and Mega Networking Members:** Free\n* **Non-members:** $27 in advance or
  $29 on event day\n\n***Not a GTApreneurs Member?*** Go here to view our m
 emberships and register: https://gtapreneurs.com/business-networking-membe
 rships\n\n**QUESTIONS ABOUT THE EVENT?**\n\nCall or text Tammy at (416) 52
 2-7770 or info@gtapreneurs.com.\n\nTo learn about Tammy Defoe's business c
 oaching services\, please go to https://gtapreneurs.com/about and https://
 gtapreneurs.com/business-coaching-toronto\n\n**EXHIBITORS:**\n\n* **Gorett
 e Marques\,** Global Bricks Realty\, https://gmarquesrealtor.com\n* **Soni
 a Kurmey\,** Arbonne\, www.soniakurmey.arbonne.com\n* **Balbir Pabila\,** 
 PPLSI\\~LegalShield\, https://bkpabila.legalshieldassociate.com\n* **Abhis
 hek Basak\,** Clerk Tech\, www.clerk-tech.com\n* **Monica Hecht\,** The Vi
 llage Hive\, www.thevillagehive.ca\n\n\\*Exhibitor tables available. Visit
  www.gtapreneurs.com/exhibitor to book a spot\n\n\\*We will EMAIL you the 
 GUEST CONTACT SHEET the day after the event by 5pm. If you don't receive i
 t in your inbox\, please check your SPAM/JUNK folder. Note: You must atten
 d the event to receive the guest contact sheet.
